President Cyril Ramaphosa is delivering his budget vote in Parliament this hour. • Editor's note: This live event has ended. You may watch a recording above. CAPE TOWN - President Cyril Ramaphosa is expected to deliver his budget vote in the National Assembly.
It's expected he will give greater detail on how promises made in his State of the Nation Address will be carried out. Opposition parties reacted with disdain and concern to Ramaphosa’s SONA, saying that he's selling dreams to South Africans.